<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038525" n="167r"/>
                    <p><lb/>En <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_V5AVH8QR">Dissertationem de Morbis <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> motu humorum circulatorio aucto oriun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dis</rs>, de qua in ultima mea <abbr>d.</abbr> 27. pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teriti mensis ad Te data <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517050105501">epistola</rs> dixi,
                    <lb/>quamque heri acceptam protinus, ut promisi, ad Te transmitto; gaudebo si
                    <lb/>aliqua in rem tuam futura in eadem deprehendes. Hac occasione Tibi signi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fico, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruelem</rs> meum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sivisse, num <rs type="letter">epistola</rs> aliqua sua <abbr>Dno.</abbr>
                                        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1343364833">Fabris</rs> inscripta, quam una cum <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_WIW87HR7">Dissertatione de Nutritione</rs> se misisse
                    <lb/>ait, eidem reddita fuerit, nec ne. Rogo, ut si nondum reddita fuerit,
                    <lb/>eam ad Bibliopolam <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1037587715">Hertz</rs> deferri cures. Audivi <abbr>Ill.mos</abbr> et <abbr>Excell.mos</abbr>
                    <lb/><abbr>D.nos</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089922930 pers_DE-588-1089586140 pers_DE-588-1089586175" type="persons">Reformatores</rs> nuper cathedras quasdam Augustissi<subst><del>no</del><add>mo</add></subst> Senatui
                    <lb/>proposuisse, nulla mentione facta <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzeri</rs>, precor itaque, ut, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                    <lb/>Tibi de bono malove rei statu comperta sunt, mihi significare non dedigne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ris.</p> <closer><salute>C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum Vale et fave.</salute> <dateline><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <date when="1718-12-08"><abbr>d.</abbr> 8. <abbr>Xbris</abbr> 1718.</date></dateline></closer>
</div>
